description.en: Zero Carbon Project is tackling climate change using the blockchain and international carbon credits. Renewable energy has responded well to the challenge but its impact has been too small and too slow. The Zero Carbon Market can deliver a quicker reduction of carbon emissions by beating both renewable energy and fossil fuels on price. As the catalyst for change, we have created a blockchain-driven economy and Zero Carbon Coin tokens as meaningful reward-based incentives for consumer action.
